    "We conclude that the current state of research has yet to sufficiently address the disagreement problem from a technical point of view.",
    "And currently, the most viable solution might be to give the decision-subject insight in the process of coming to explanations.",
    "Providing transparency should ensure that decision-makers can be held accountable for their actions.",
    "Ideally, such a principle would be enforced by regulation.",
    "This is particularly crucial in high-risk decision-making scenarios where individuals bear the consequences of algorithmic processes."
